I was thinking along this same path. Especially with the new proposed section and aside tags. It would be great to have a 'for' attribute to specify which section the aside pertains to. I suppose this could be achieved by simply nesting the elements as well, but I would agree with haka that a general purpose semantic connector would be useful in some circumstances.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=200">mmilo</a> — Tue Dec 04, 2007 6:08 am</p><hr />
